cs.DL, cs.IR, cs.CR, cs.CY, cs.SI 

The paper focuses on the analysis of current publication trends in gold Open Access (OA) in the context of academic publishing, which is closely related to digital libraries (cs.DL) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The analysis also involves investigating the research output produced by different units of analysis, including disciplinary differences (cs.CR), national idiosyncrasies (cs.CY), and citation differences between OA and non-OA publications (cs.SI).
